  "texts": [
    "Can be a direction or a specific location (gaze point).",
    "Head boxed eye-tracker setup An eye-tracker setup where the participant's head can move within a frustum (also known as the headbox).",
    "Head-free eye-tracker setup An eye-tracker setup where the participant's head can move freely.",
    "What is an eye tracker Head-restricted eye-tracker setup An eye-tracker setup where the participant's head is restricted.",
    "What is an eye tracker Precision (deg) How dispersed estimated gaze locations are."
